text: The List for Sandžak (Bosnian/Serbian: Lista za Sandžak / Листа за Санџак) is a minority coalition, representing ethnic Bosniaks in Serbia. It is led by Sulejman Ugljanin and includes: * Party of Democratic Action of Sandžak * Bosniak Democratic Party of Sandžak * Social Liberal Party of Sandžak At the latest legislative election in 2007, it has won two seats in the parliament. title: List for Sandžak
